column5: What date is the opening of the 2014 Walleye season in Zone 4, Indian Lake Ignace, Ontario. I'm unable to download the MNR's regulations PDF.
Larry, are you planning on a trip to Gummy Land????

Guy says he has a cabin open June 7-14, so I'm going to see if Kim M. still wants to go up, if not I'll probably take the camper and go up by myself. I hear you had one of your ball-joints replaced, how is your recovery going? It'll be a year next month since I had mine done and everything is going fine. Are you and your group planning a trip?
Larry, I sent you a pm.....(upper righthand corner of screen)
